#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ktuberling; a simple constructor game suitable for children and adults "
#| "alike. The idea of the game is based around a once popular doll making "
#| "concept. A potato was decorated with various small artifacts to make it "
#| "look more like a tiny person. &ktuberling; however, goes much further in "
#| "terms of content and adds a surprising variety of different themes."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktuberling; is a simple constructor game suitable for children and "
"adults alike. The idea of the game is based around a once popular doll "
"making concept. A potato was decorated with various small artifacts to make "
"it look more like a tiny person. &i18n-ktuberling; however, goes much "
"further in terms of content and adds a surprising variety of different "
"themes."
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; jednostavna graditeljska igra pogodna kako za djecu tako i za "
"odrasle. Ideja igre zasniva se na nekad popularnom konceptu pravljenja "
"lutaka. Krompir je bio ukrašen sa različitim malim rukotvorinama kako bi "
"više ličio na sićušnu osobu. &ktuberling; međutim, ide puno dalje u pogledu "
"sadržaja i dodaje iznenađujuću raznovrsnost različitih tema."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako Igrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ktuberling; is a game intended for small children. Of course, it may be "
#| "suitable for adults who have remained young at heart."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktuberling; is a game intended for small children. Of course, it may "
"be suitable for adults who have remained young at heart."
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; je igra namijenjena maloj djeci. Naravno, može biti pogodna za "
"odrasle koji su ostali mladi u srcu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is a <quote>potato editor</quote>. That means that you can drag and drop "
"eyes, mouths, mustache, and other parts of face and goodies onto a potato-"
"like guy. Similarly, you have other playgrounds with different themes."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je <quote>uređivač krompira</quote>. To znači da možete stavljati i "
"skidati oči, usta, brkove i druge dijelove lica i stvarčice na momka koji "
"iči na krompir. Slično tome imate druga igrališta sa raličitim temama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no winner for the game. The only purpose is to make the funniest "
"faces you can."
msgstr ""
"Nema pobjednika u ovoj igri. Jedini cilj je napraviti što zabavnija lica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&ktuberling; can also <quote>speak</quote>. It will spell out the name of "
#| "the objects you drag and drop. It will <quote>speak</quote> in a language "
#| "that you can choose. You can even use it to learn a bit of vocabulary in "
#| "foreign languages."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktuberling; can also <quote>speak</quote>. It will spell out the name "
"of the objects you drag and drop. It will <quote>speak</quote> in a language "
"that you can choose. You can even use it to learn a bit of vocabulary in "
"foreign languages."
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; može takođe <quote>govoriti</quote>. On će sricati ime objekta "
"koji dovlačite i spuštate. On će <quote>govoriti</quote> na jeziku koji "
"možete odabrati. Možete ga čak koristiti da pomalo učite vokabular na "
"stranim jezicima."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila i Savjeti"

