#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two areas in the main window:"
msgstr "Postoje dvije oblasti na glavnom prozoru:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>Playground</quote> area."
msgstr "<quote>Igralište</quote> oblast."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Objects</quote> area, where you select objects to place on your "
"playground."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Objekti</quote> oblast, gdje možete odabrati objekte da ih smjestite "
"na svoje igralište."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An actual look of the application screen may change depending on a "
"<quote>playground</quote> selected."
msgstr ""
"Trenutni izgled ekrana za aplikaciju može se mijenjati zavisno od "
"<quote>igrališta</quote> koje je odabrano."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:145
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Main Window of &ktuberling;"
msgid "Main Window of &i18n-ktuberling;"
msgstr "Glavni Prozor &ktuberling;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Glavni Prozor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Placing an Object"
msgstr "Postavljanje Objekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To drag an object, move the mouse pointer to the <quote>objects</quote> area "
"and click on it. Then move it to the <quote>playground</quote> area and "
"click again."
msgstr ""
"Da se dovuče objekt, pomjerite strelicu miša na <quote>objekti </quote> "
"oblast i kliknite na nju. Onda je pomjerite na <quote>igralište</quote> "
"oblast i ponovo kliknite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Size of the objects may change while dragging. Some of the oversized "
#| "objects have been scaled down to feet into the “objects” area."
msgid ""
"Size of the objects may change while dragging. Some of the oversized objects "
"have been scaled down to feet into the <quote>objects</quote> area."
msgstr ""
"Veličina objekata može se mijenjati dok povlačite. Neki od prevelikih "
"objekata su smanjeni da pristaju u \"objekti\" oblast."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving an Object"
msgstr "Pomjeranje Objekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once dropped in the <quote>playground</quote> area, an object can be moved. "
"Just click on the object to select it, move it to the new place and click "
"again to drop it. When you drop it, it goes on top of other objects that "
"were partially hiding it. This trick is useful for getting the glasses and "
"eyes placed correctly."
msgstr ""
"Kad je jednom smješten u <quote>igralište</quote>oblast, objekat se može "
"pomjerati. Samo klinite na objekat da ga selektirate, pomjerite ga na novo "
"mjesto i ponovo kliknite da ga pustite.  Kadaga pustite, one ide iznad "
"drugih objekata koji su ga djelimično sakrivali. Ovaj trik je koristan da se "
"ispravno postave oči i naočale."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removing an Object"
msgstr "Uklanjanje Objekta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an object that has been dropped in the <quote>playground</quote> "
"area, drag it back from the <quote>playground</quote> area to the "
"<quote>objects</quote> area."
msgstr ""
"Da se ukloni objekat koji je spušten u <quote>igralište</quote> oblast, "
"povucite ga natrag iz <quote>igralište</quote> oblasti u <quote>objekti</"
"quote> oblast."

