#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim promijeniti izgled igre. Mogu li to uraditi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes you can. Refer to <link linkend=\"theme_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da, možete. Pogledajte <link linkend=\"theme_change\">this</link> dio  "
"'Pregled Izgleda' za detalje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Mogu li koristiti tastature da igram ovu igru?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. Ovu igru ne možetee igrati sa tastaturom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have made a great picture and I want to share it with my friends. Can I "
"save it as an image?"
msgstr ""
"Napravio sam odličnu sliku i želim je podijliti sa mojim prijeteljima. Mogu "
"li je snimiti kao sliku?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To save the current session as an image refer to <link linkend=\"game-"
"save-as-picture\">this</link> section of 'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Da. Da bi ste snimili trenutnu sesiju kao sliku otiđite na <link linkend="
"\"game-save-as-picture\">this</link> dio o 'Pregledu Izgleda' za detalje."

